From: Nunchi Operators <nunchi@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 18:15:05 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] discord: append exact native facts per delivered message

The rendered channel tag omits the exact author ID, bot flag, mention
IDs, guild, and reply reference even though the gateway payload has
them. Append those facts as one JSON line per delivered message to
STATE_DIR/nunchi-native-events.jsonl so a Nunchi V2 consumer can bind
exact identity and native relations without inferring them from display
names or prose. Facts the transport does not synchronously hold (the
referenced message's author and content) are recorded as absent rather
than fetched or guessed. Size-capped with one rotation generation.
---
 server.ts | 43 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-
 1 file changed, 42 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/server.ts b/server.ts
index 9162be1..c226b57 100644
--- a/server.ts
+++ b/server.ts
@@ -31,7 +31,7 @@ import {
 } from 'discord.js'
